Program: Great Lives
Title: Lord Longford
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00cvbkm
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 3 Feb 2017
Series of biographical discussions with Matthew Parris. Jon Snow argues the case for the prison reform campaigner and former member of Attlee's cabinet. He is assisted by Longford's daughter Rachel Billington and his biographer Peter Stanford.